About us
Welcome to our RV park!
In the surrounding area are marinas, natural springs, beaches, river fishing, fishing off a pier, boat launch, canoeing, river rafting, biking and golf courses. Whether you explore all the area has to offer, or just relax beneath the tall shady oak trees, Shady Oaks RV Park is the perfect home base for your vacation. You get the best of both worlds, local attractions, outdoor recreation and a peaceful, quiet, beautiful, clean RV park.
Our RV park is centrally located to Gainesville, Perry, and Lake City. We are only 70 miles from Ocala, FL, 162 miles from Tampa, FL and 117 miles from Jacksonville, FL. Chiefland, FL is only a short 17 miles where you can find a WalMart, Tractor Supply, Bealls Outlet, Winn Dixie, and many restaurants and fast food places. 130 miles from historic St. Augustine, 155 miles from the famous Daytona Beach. 148 miles to Disney World. 50 miles from the home of the University of Florida Gators, in Gainesville, FL. Major VA hospitals are located in Gainesville and Lake City. An excellent out patient VA clinic is located in Perry. We are just 3 miles from Cross City, which has a Family Dollar, Dollar General, Save-a-Lot grocery store, a Post Office, several banks, several fast food places and some dine in places that offer Country Cooking, Mexican or Chinese.
